On the hunt for the holy grail of mascaras that won’t hurt your wallet? It’s tough—there are almost endless mascaras available offering longer, fuller or darker lashes claiming they’re the best. So which ones really reign supreme? That depends all on your specific needs. We have rounded up the best-reviewed mascaras you can find at Walmart offering a variety of features. And they’re all under $12! HuffPost receives a share from retailers on this page. Every item is independently selected by the HuffPost Shopping team. Prices and availability are subject to change.